dcterms:description: This dataset contains 7 kinds of encrypted traffic, which can be divided into categories such as Chat, Email, File Transfer, P2P, Streaming, VoIP, and Browsing. For simplicity, the Browsing category is removed as it includes traffic from all other classes.
